Package de.weltraumschaf.jebnf.gfx.shapes.other

All other railroad shapes package.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AbstractEndpointShape Endpoint shapes are either the start or the end of a single railroad line.
CurveShape Draw curves.
EndShape  
ForkShape Forks are a combination of either a "straight shape" with direction StraightShape.Directions.NORT_SOUTH or StraightShape.Directions.WEST_EAST shape and a "curve shape" with direction CurveShape.Directions#North_EAST, CurveShape.Directions#North_WEST, CurveShape.Directions.SOUTH_EAST, or CurveShape.Directions.SOUTH_WEST.
RectangularShape RectangularShape shape.
StartShape  
StraightShape Paints a straight line either from north to south or from west to east.
TestShape Paint blue dots on each second pixel.
 

Enum Summary
CurveShape.Directions Type of curve railroad shapes.
StraightShape.Directions Type of straight railroad shapes.
